org.apache.freemarker.core.templateresolver

Class TemplateResolverDependencies

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.freemarker.core.templateresolver.TemplateResolverDependencies

  • public abstract class TemplateResolverDependencies
extends Object
    Stores the dependencies of a TemplateResolver. See TemplateResolver for more. This is normally implemented by FreeMarker internally.
